column2: SELECT TOP # /* PhotoObj table*/  p.objid,round(p.ra,#) as ra,round(p.dec,#) as dec,round(p.u,#) as PhotoOb_u,  round(p.g,#) as PhotoOb_g,round(p.r,#) as PhotoOb_r,round(p.i,#) as   PhotoOb_i,round(p.z,#) as PhotoObj_z, p.type, /*specObj table*/  s.specobjid, s.class, s.subClass, round(s.z,#) as spec_redshift,  round(s.zErr,#) as spec_redshift_Err,round(s.zWarning,#) as Spec_redshift_Warning, /* Photomtric redshift table*/  round(pz.z,#) As Photo_Z, round(pz.zErr,#) AS Photo_Err FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN Photoz as pz ON pz.objID=p.objid
